- ‚úÖ **Use semantic HTML**: `<strong>`, `<em>`, `<mark>`
- ‚úÖ **Limit emphasis**: Don't bold everything
- ‚úÖ **Consistent formatting**: Apply styles consistently
- ‚úÖ **Readable paragraphs**: Use spacing between paragraphs

